description: SpareBank 1 Nordmøre provides various banking products and services in Norway. The company offers business insurance products, including vehicle and machinery, value and building, employee and personnel, and farm and agricultural insurance; personal insurance products, such as car, home, personal, pet, vehicle, travel, and valuables insurance products; pension products; bank cards; payment and debt collection services; and mobile and online banking services. It also provides bank guarantees, operating credit products for agriculture, and factoring and leasing products and services, as well as savings and deposit accounts, refinancing, and mortgage services. SpareBank 1 Nordmøre was founded in 1835 and is based in Kristiansund, Norway. SpareBank 1 Nordmøre is a subsidiary of SpareBank 1 Gruppen AS.
